I hear complaint that programs that did work a few months ago do not
work recently.  I've forgotten to explain a change in primitive body
construction. Segment parameter now needs to specify with a keyword.
You can also give color and name attributes to a body.

(make-cube x y z &key color name)
(make-cylinder radius height &key (segments 12) color name)

Try (documentation 'make-cylinder), etc.

